!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta(content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv='Content-Type')
  %body
    %h1{style: 'text-align:center'}
      Thank You

    %p Pack 4496 on Bainbridge Island thanks you for your support and in helping a Scout earn his way to Summer Camp.

    %p We have received your order and expect to deliver it by November 10, 2016.

    %h2 Your Order
    %ul
      - total = 0
      - @take_order.take_order_line_items.each do |line_item|
        %li
          = line_item.product.name
          = surround("(", ")") do
            = line_item.quantity
          - value = line_item.quantity * line_item.product.retail_price
          = number_to_currency(value)
          - total += value
      %li
        Amount due:
        = number_to_currency(total)

      %li
        - if @take_order.payment_account_id == 6
          Please pay on delivery
        - else
          PAID IN FULL. Thank you!

    %p
      If you have any questions, you can reach us at
      = mail_to("pack4496@gmail.com")